### ✅ CORRECT: Proper Authorization Pattern

```python
# ✅ GOOD: Proper authorization flow
class GoodTradingEngine:
    async def execute_trade(self, request: TradingDecisionRequest):
        # Step 1: Get authorization (MANDATORY per Rule 3)
        authorization = await self.risk_manager.authorize_trading_decision(request)
        
        if authorization.authorization_level == AuthorizationLevel.REJECTED:
            return None
        
        # Step 2: Execute ONLY with authorization
        result = await self._execute_authorized(authorization)
        
        # Step 3: Report result back to RiskManager
        await self.risk_manager.on_execution_complete(authorization.authorization_id, result)
        
        return result
